---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const seo = {
  title: 'Specialty Facials | D-Essence Wellness',
  description:
    'Advanced, customized facials using medical-grade actives and device-assisted steps—LED, oxygen, microcurrent, ultrasound—to target acne, discoloration, dehydration, sensitivity, and early aging.',
  canonical: '/services/specialty-facials/',
  type: 'website',
  jsonLd: [
    {
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'Service',
      name: 'Specialty Facials',
      serviceType: 'Facial',
      areaServed: 'New Windsor, New York',
      provider: {
        '@type': 'MedicalBusiness',
        name: 'D-Essence Wellness',
        address: {
          '@type': 'PostalAddress',
          streetAddress: '871 Blooming Grove Turnpike Suite 102',
          addressLocality: 'New Windsor',
          addressRegion: 'NY',
          postalCode: '12553',
          addressCountry: 'US'
        }
      },
      url: 'https://dessencewellness.com/services/specialty-facials/'
    }
  ]
};
---

<BaseLayout seo={seo}>
  <!-- ===== HERO (dark) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-neutral-950 text-white">
    <div class="container pt-28 pb-10 max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/60">
        <span>Services</span><span class="opacity-40">•</span><span>Advanced Skin Care</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Specialty Facials</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/80">
        Device-assisted, multi-step facials that go beyond cleansing—pairing targeted actives with
        LED, oxygen, microcurrent, ultrasound and more to address acne, discoloration, dehydration,
        sensitivity, and early signs of aging.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Targets</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Acne • Pigment • Sensitivity</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Approach</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Personalized, multi-step</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Session time</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">~45–90 min</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-white/5 ring-1 ring-white/10 p-3">
          <div class="text-white/70">Downtime</div>
          <div class="mt-0.5 font-medium">Minimal (varies)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== CONTENT (white) ===== -->
  <section class="bg-white text-neutral-900">
    <div class="container py-12 sm:py-14">
      <!-- Overview -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Overview</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Specialty facials are advanced protocols tailored to your skin’s current needs. They combine
            professional-strength formulations with technologies like LED light therapy, ultrasound infusion,
            microcurrent, oxygen application, or gentle enzymatic peels to deliver visible results with
            little to no downtime.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Each treatment is built from your consultation: we assess skin health, sensitivities, and goals,
            then stack precise steps—cleanse, exfoliate, targeted actives, device work, mask, and finishing care.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-medium">Key benefits</h3>
            <ul class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-sm text-neutral-700">
              {[
                'Brighter, more even tone',
                'Refined texture and pores',
                'Hydration and barrier support',
                'Calms redness and sensitivity',
                'Targets acne and congestion',
                'Softens early lines',
              ].map(item => (
                <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none">
                    <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                  </svg>
                  <span>{item}</span>
                </li>
              ))}
            </ul>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
              Benefits vary by protocol and skin type; consistent care and sun protection improve longevity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Types / menu of facials -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Popular specialty options</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          {[
            {
              name: 'Vitamin C Antioxidant Facial',
              does: 'High-potency antioxidants and infusion methods to revive dull, photoexposed skin.',
              best: 'Dull tone, sun damage, early discoloration'
            },
            {
              name: 'Hydrating HA Facial',
              does: 'Layered humectants and barrier-repair actives to replenish moisture and comfort.',
              best: 'Dry, dehydrated, mature or post-procedure skin'
            },
            {
              name: 'LED Light Therapy Facial',
              does: 'Red/near-IR for collagen support; blue LED to calm acne-prone skin.',
              best: 'Acne, redness, maintenance of collagen'
            },
            {
              name: 'Oxygen Infusion Facial',
              does: 'Pressurized oxygen delivers soothing serums for instant glow and refresh.',
              best: 'Fatigued, devitalized, travel-stressed skin'
            },
            {
              name: 'Microcurrent Tone-Up',
              does: 'Low-level electrical current to gently stimulate and contour.',
              best: 'Mild laxity, contour refinement'
            },
            {
              name: 'Enzyme Glow Facial',
              does: 'Papaya/pineapple enzymes for gentle exfoliation without harsh acids.',
              best: 'Sensitive skin needing smoothness'
            },
            {
              name: 'Calming Facial (Sensitive/Rosacea)',
              does: 'Aloe, centella, peptide complexes and cooling masks to reduce reactivity.',
              best: 'Reactive, redness-prone, sensitized skin'
            },
            {
              name: 'Brightening Facial',
              does: 'Actives like kojic, vitamin C, and supportive exfoliation for spots.',
              best: 'Sun spots, uneven tone, mild melasma (with guidance)'
            },
            {
              name: 'Custom Blend',
              does: 'Mixed modalities in one session to match multiple priorities.',
              best: 'Combination concerns; event prep'
            }
          ].map(card => (
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">{card.name}</div>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-neutral-700">{card.does}</p>
              <div class="mt-2 text-xs text-neutral-500">Best for: {card.best}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          Devices and actives are selected to your skin tone and tolerance. Some options may be deferred during pregnancy/lactation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- What to expect -->
      <div class="mt-12 grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">What to expect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700">
            Your session blends comfort and clinical precision. Plans may include double cleanse, gentle exfoliation,
            targeted serums, device steps (LED, ultrasound, oxygen, microcurrent), a high-performance mask, and
            finishing care with SPF.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Consultation</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Skin history, sensitivities, current routine, and goals.</li>
                <li>Visual analysis: tone, texture, hydration, reactivity.</li>
                <li>Patch testing for stronger actives if needed.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">During treatment</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Comfort-first approach with calibrated steps.</li>
                <li>Technologies applied based on tolerance and goals.</li>
                <li>Typical duration: ~45–90 minutes.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5 sm:col-span-2">
              <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Results timeline</div>
              <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
                <li>Immediate: fresher glow and smoother feel.</li>
                <li>Following days: texture and tone continue to refine.</li>
                <li>Series: cumulative firming and clarity with regular visits.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Aftercare -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Aftercare</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Broad-spectrum SPF; minimize direct sun exposure.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Gentle cleanser and non-irritating moisturizer.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Skip harsh actives for 24–48 hours (or as advised).
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <ul class="text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Avoid steam/sauna and strenuous heat the same day.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Do not over-exfoliate; let any flaking resolve naturally.
              </li>
              <li class="inline-flex items-start gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                Use the recommended follow-up products for best results.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Safety -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Safety & considerations</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-neutral-700">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Common, temporary effects</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Mild redness or warmth</li>
              <li>Transient sensitivity or tightness</li>
              <li>Occasional light flaking (depending on actives)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Reduce risk</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Customize intensity for sensitive skin</li>
              <li>Sun protection to avoid post-inflammatory pigment</li>
              <li>Disclose allergies; patch test when appropriate</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Who may need to wait</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Active infection, inflamed acne, or open lesions</li>
              <li>Recent strong peels/lasers; allow recovery first</li>
              <li>Photosensitizing medications (per provider guidance)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <div class="text-sm font-medium text-neutral-900">Special cases</div>
            <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-700 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Pregnancy/lactation—use conservative protocols</li>
              <li>Known ingredient allergies—avoid triggers</li>
              <li>Darker tones—favor gentle, pigment-safe steps</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">FAQ</h2>
        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4">
          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">How many sessions will I need?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Many clients start with a series of 3–6 treatments, then shift to monthly or seasonal maintenance based on goals.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Will I see immediate results?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Expect glow and softness right away. Texture, clarity, and firmness build over days—and compound with a plan.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Does it hurt?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Most steps are comfortable. Mild tingling or warmth can occur with certain actives or devices and is kept within tolerance.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Can I combine with other treatments?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Yes—facials often pair well with microneedling, gentle peels, or lasers. We’ll coordinate timing to protect your barrier.
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="group rounded-xl bg-white ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-5">
            <summary class="list-none cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="font-medium text-neutral-900">Are results permanent?</span>
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M5.8 7.3a1 1 0 011.4 0L10 10.1l2.8-2.8a1 1 0 111.4 1.4l-3.5 3.5a1 1 0 01-1.4 0L5.8 8.7a1 1 0 010-1.4z"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <p class="mt-3 text-neutral-700 text-sm">
              Improvements are real but not permanent; ongoing care and sun protection help maintain outcomes over time.
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-50 ring-1 ring-neutral-200 p-6 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="text-sm text-neutral-700">
            Ready to design a facial plan around your skin’s priorities?
          </div>
          <a href="/contact-us/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-neutral-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm hover:bg-neutral-800 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-neutral-300">
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
